snippet.title: No Respite from Long Queues to People as Note Ban Goes on to 19th Day

localized.description:
Demonetisation: There is no respite from long queues to people as note ban goes on to 19th day. All banks are closed on this weekend and hence peoples are depend on ATMs only to withdraw cash.
